data.description: Beautiful Canyon Heights Home! This lovely home is located among rolling foothills just east of Canyon Lake. Enjoy the mountain views from the spacious backyard and large covered patio. The interior has 3 bedrooms with an optional 4th bedroom/office. The home features a huge luxurious master suite with sitting area, walk in closet and stunning views of the mountain tops. Sit by the fireplace in the spacious family room which has an open flow to the kitchen and separate living room. LOW HOA!
